Package au.csiro.pathling.library.io.sink

Interface DataSink

All Known Implementing Classes:
CatalogSink, DatabaseSink, DeltaSink, NdjsonSink, ParquetSink
public interface DataSink
Represents a data sink that knows how to read data from a DataSource and write it to some form of persistence.
